thread.title: Florida governor proposes tighter gun restrictions

title: Florida governor proposes tighter gun restrictions
text:
Florida governor proposes tighter gun restrictions Friday, February 23, 2018 - 00:42 
Florida Governor Rick Scott announced a proposal on Friday to increase restrictions on buying guns and to strengthen school safety measures after a gunman killed 17 people at a high school in the state last week. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
